{
  "stem": "24364.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we knew we were going with an illegal transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were told it would take between six and 12 months before we were-- we would be ready.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, obviously September the 1st, the war started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that changed things drastically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- we were all sent home and told that they are going to put us on the next transport available.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during-- so we were sent home sometime, I think the middle of September, I believe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it took a while before everything was arranged.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next three months, we were preparing papers, paying taxes, getting passports, being interviewed by the Gestapo, and-- and-- and-- and.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some people from our group, they were denied passports, out of some technical reasons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know whether their parents-- they owned something, and they didn't want to give it up or some people had some problems with finances.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I know that about three or four of our group didn't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I had no difficulties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after rumors were flying for weeks, changing dates of our departure constantly, finally the departure was set for December the 15th, 1939.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after the right paper, legal immigration to Israel was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Zionist organizations came up with Aliyah Bet, which was illegal from the point of view of the Palestine authorities but legal from the point of view of the Zionist authorities.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So any Aliyah Bet transport was accepted in Israel-- if they managed to get there-- was accepted by the Zionist authorities as a legal immigration.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were a couple of transports, which went before us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our transport was supposed to leave illegally, from the German point of view and from the British point of view, but legally from the Zionist point of view.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
